(1945, 1, '2025-02-17 07:13:46', '2025-02-17 07:13:46', 'This content is before the <a title=\"The More Tag\" href=\"https://en.support.wordpress.com/splitting-content/more-tag/\" target=\"_blank\">more tag</a>.\n\nRight after this sentence should be a \"continue reading\" button of some sort on list pages of themes that show full content. It won\'t show on single pages or on themes showing excerpts.\n\n<!--more-->\n\nAnd this content is after the more tag. (which should be the anchor link for when the button is clicked)', 'Template: More Tag', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '996-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-02-17 07:13:46', '2025-02-17 07:13:46', '', 996, 'http://localhost:8080/subhajit/?p=1945', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
